chart.name: Network I/O bytes/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('network.bytes_in', rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('network.bytes_out', rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.name: Total Network I/O bytes/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('network.bytes_in', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('network.bytes_out', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Mutations/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('opcounter.insert', rollup='latest').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('opcounter.update', rollup='latest').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A+B).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Queries/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('opcounter.query', rollup='latest').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Page Faults/Sec
chart.programText:
A = data('extra_info.page_faults', rollup='latest').sum(by=['replica_set_name']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Deletes/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('opcounter.delete', rollup='latest').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=95).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.description: Number of MongoDB processes in cluster
chart.name: # Processes
Storage, Index, Data Size
chart.programText:
A = data('storage_size', rollup='latest', maxExtrapolations=2).publish(label='A')
B = data('index_size', rollup='latest', maxExtrapolations=2).publish(label='B')
C = data('data_size', rollup='latest', maxExtrapolations=2).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Total Global Lock Queued Operations
chart.programText:
A = data('global_lock.current_queue.readers', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('global_lock.current_queue.writers', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')

chart.description: The time a secondary has to replicate the primary oplog
chart.name: Replication Headrooms
Mutations/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('opcounter.insert', rollup='latest').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('opcounter.update', rollup='latest').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A+B).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A+B).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A+B).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A+B).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')
G = (A+B).max().publish(label='G')

chart.description: Bottom 5 of the times each secondary process has to replicate the primary oplog
chart.name: Bottom 5 Replication Headrooms
Global Lock Queued Operations
chart.programText:
A = data('global_lock.current_queue.readers', rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('global_lock.current_queue.writers', rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.name: Hosts with Largest Storage, Index, Data Size
chart.programText:
A = data('storage_size', rollup='latest', maxExtrapolations=2).top(count=1).sum(by=['host', 'type_name']).publish(label='A')
B = data('index_size', rollup='latest', maxExtrapolations=2).top(count=1).sum(by=['host', 'type_name']).publish(label='B')
C = data('data_size', rollup='latest', maxExtrapolations=2).top(count=1).sum(by=['host', 'type_name']).publish(label='C')
